{"tid":1777991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵沙田站內掟月餅罐 女子被加控暴動罪 打立場姐姐個西瓜佬陳志祥仲未拉到","createTime":"2019-12-10T15:01:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T16:24:41.000Z","uid":278443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e1cae2f3a7c9e5e1484fd06e39e0d8da225762","tid":1777991,"uid":278443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"《抗暴之戰》港鐵沙田站內掟月餅罐 女子被加控暴動罪 <br />\n<br />\n市民9月初發動「和你塞3.0」，及後有示威者聚集港鐵沙田站，其間防暴警察進入站內驅散，雙方爆發衝突。一名女經理被指向警員掟月餅罐，早前被控襲警罪。案件今在東區裁判法院再訊，控方加控涉案女經理一項暴動罪，並將襲警罪中的警員姓名隱去，改為只顯示其職級及警員編號。裁判官林子勤應控方申請，將案件押後至明年1月14日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方透露，下次聆訊會申請將本案、即被告劉婉玲（45歲）所涉案件，與早前任職活動策劃員的被告謝嘉綸（42歲）被控暴動一案合併，案件將轉介至區域法院審理。控方亦申請修改劉及謝各自面對的暴動罪，將對方名字加入控罪詳情中。<br />\n<br />\n控方透露，下次聆訊會申請將本案、即被告劉婉玲（45歲）所涉案件，與早前任職活動策劃員的被告謝嘉綸（42歲）被控暴動一案合併，案件將轉介至區域法院審理。控方亦申請修改劉及謝各自面對的暴動罪，將對方名字加入控罪詳情中。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：ESCC2129、2392/19】<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191210&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60363370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191210%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60363370&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=0675eba9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191210%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60363370&h=1509e159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191210&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60363370</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要幫呢幾位手足呀，幫推啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">掉月餅就暴動 恐襲就無野 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n721 元朗站恐怖襲擊果幾百個班暴徒仲未拉到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打立場姐姐個陳志祥都未拉到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人 報仇</span>"},{"pid":"efb8b73d6a936bc374d0922add2ac7ce53672286","tid":1777991,"uid":278443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"掉月餅罐暴動 恐襲無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd67fb18948ed1bf1dcea98a6fc1332550b7aff9","tid":1777991,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9f5ba1a263dfab57736009953717f0bdece95e22","tid":1777991,"uid":278443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:04:50.000Z","msg":"掉月餅罐暴動 恐襲無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944a8a7f3c07c8772564686876b325320de47803","tid":1777991,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35RcTVr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35RcTVr.jpg&h=deeb3702&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b16caa9eca9ed8916095a67ea4e36fe1f954d108","tid":1777991,"uid":197163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"944a8a7f3c07c8772564686876b325320de47803","tid":1777991,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35RcTVr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35RcTVr.jpg&h=deeb3702&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"呢個左膠比人拉左未？"},{"pid":"0e8bd9b8f71d2f7dcd2ed2254ad80b7be54b6640","tid":1777991,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"721 黑幫拉得幾個，得 6 個暴動罪，到今日都未上庭，律政司快D仆街死 <img src=\"/asset